articles.title: Underdog Australia counting on home crowd vs. England: 'They're going to be vital' - FOX Sports
articles.description: On paper, Australia is facing long odds against mighty England — but this game won't be played on paper; it'll be played in front of 80,000 raucous Aussie fans.
articles.content:
